This License is not compatible with proprietary licenses or licenses that permit Commercial Use by non-Permitted Entities. Any attempt to combine this Program with software under such licenses, in a way that would require the distribution of this Program under those licenses, is expressly prohibited.

Works licensed under GPL-2.0 or GPL-3.0 may be incorporated into software governed by this License by Permitted Entities, provided that the resulting combined work is governed entirely by this License and not redistributed to non-Permitted Entities for commercial purposes.

